1
00:00:12,360 --> 00:00:12,760
Like this.

2
00:00:13,440 --> 00:00:14,840
I'll let you try a grappling move.

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:15,440
Come on.

4
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:28,280
You didn't pin me down.

5
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:32,480
Actually,

6
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:36,600
that time He Qi released the poison smoke,

7
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:39,560
even though you were shivering,

8
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:42,720
you still stood in front of me without hesitation.

9
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,280
I knew from that moment on,

10
00:00:46,480 --> 00:00:47,720
in this world,

11
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:50,280
there will never be another person

12
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,640
who would risk their life for me like that.

13
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:53,160
Miss.

14
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:54,480
Hold your breath.

15
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:56,920
Watch out.

16
00:01:04,520 --> 00:01:05,880
If there is a next time,

17
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:08,320
I will still stand in front of you.

18
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,360
I believe you.

19
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:13,760
But I need time.

20
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:14,920
Okay.

21
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:29,400
Did I scare you?

22
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:30,400
No.

23
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:33,160
I brought you a folding chair.

24
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,080
Squatting like that isn't good for you.

25
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,040
Here, try this.

26
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,320
Thank you.

27
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,560
And I...

28
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,280
brought some food for the little ants.

29
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:40,960
Look.

30
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,000
It's so exquisite.

31
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,560
You're so good.

32
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:49,520
They all think that me watching small animals all day

33
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,800
makes me look like a fool.

34
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:51,920
Who said that?

35
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,680
I'll go beat him up.

36
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:53,960
Da Qiang.

37
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:57,960
Maybe...

38
00:01:58,080 --> 00:02:00,240
he indeed needs some proper exercise.

39
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,480
But I think you are the

40
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,480
smartest woman in the world.

41
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:07,120
By the way,

42
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:07,800
I...

43
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,240
brought you a gift.

44
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:11,880
Look.

45
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:12,920
What is this?

46
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,280
What is this?

47
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,000
I went to catch river clams

48
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:18,280
and ground them into pearl powder.

49
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,560
It whitens skin and protects against the sun.

50
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,440
It's especially good for girls.

51
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,880
Won't the river clams feel pain?

52
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:25,720
Maybe...

53
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,520
a little.

54
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,080
Then apologize.

55
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:28,800
I'm sorry.

56
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,400
Apologize to it.

57
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,960
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

58
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,240
I ground you into powder.

59
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:34,800
I'm sorry.

60
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,360
I forgive you on behalf of the clam.

61
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,440
Don't do it again next time.

62
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,160
You know?

63
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:39,800
I won't.

64
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,440
We must cherish small animals.

65
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:43,920
Cherish small animals.

66
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,280
This is the Ant King.

67
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,240
He's very bad.

68
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,520
He has many mistresses.

69
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,760
You aren't allowed to be like that.

70
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,320
The Ant King is female.

71
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,000
Really?

72
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,040
Then she's amazing.

73
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,760
She collected so many little boys.

74
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,160
So amazing.

75
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,480
Really amazing.

76
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,120
Tell me,

77
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,440
do you have nothing better to do?

78
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,200
Bringing a vat of lousy shrimp

79
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,160
all the way here like it's a treasure?

80
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:28,560
They breed so fast,

81
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,720
you can't even catch them all.

82
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,040
You can't catch them all.

83
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,480
What do you know?

84
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,320
It's a strategy.

85
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,120
A scheme.

86
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,480
Just to lure you spies

87
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,840
out of the Kingdom of Dawei.

88
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,360
Keep bragging about your "scheme."

89
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,360
Anyway,

90
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:42,240
we've finished our quota for today.

91
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,080
You guys...

92
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,080
still have a long way to go, right?

93
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,160
Hurry up

94
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:45,920
and go catch shrimp.

95
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:46,800
Why should we catch shrimp?

96
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,320
Catch what shrimp?

97
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,680
It's your Daye Kingdom that catches shrimp!

98
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,560
You all catch shrimp!

99
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,720
Catch shrimp!

100
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,360
Back to the room.

101
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,680
Let's go rest.

102
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:53,920
Despicable.

103
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,040
So despicable.

104
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,440
If I knew kung fu, I'd kill him.

105
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,000
Let's go.

106
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:03,400
Let's go catch shrimp.

107
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:06,960
Strategist,

108
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,320
why is their quota five catties,

109
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,520
while ours is a hundred?

110
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,440
Don't worry about that.

111
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,200
Now, regarding this whole matter,

112
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,720
we need to get to the root of it.

113
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,640
The root of it?

114
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,000
Back when my parents gave birth to me...

115
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:19,200
That's too far back.

116
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:21,120
Then where do we start?

117
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,200
Think about why we set out.

118
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:25,880
And think about

119
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,280
why the Lord was convinced

120
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,800
this Divine object could clear silt.

121
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,560
Who gave him that idea?

122
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,280
And why did we

123
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,320
get involved in this mess?

124
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,520
Why did Miss Aqin appear at that time?

125
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,720
And why was Yu Tong hit by a carriage?

126
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,760
Why did the vat fall into the lake?

127
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:40,520
And why are we

128
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,520
trapped in this

129
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,960
inescapable small mountain village?

130
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,720
And who made us start infighting?

131
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,680
In the end, who exactly wants to harm me?

132
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,960
Dawei?

133
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,200
So who is it then?

134
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:52,400
The vat.

135
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,440
Strategist.

136
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,920
So our primary task now

137
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,280
is to fish the vat out.

138
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,680
I've already fished the vat out.

139
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,760
After fishing the vat out,

140
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,680
we have to find a place to hide it.

141
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,800
Right. We live together every day,

142
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,640
so how do we hide it?

143
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,680
I have long since hidden the vat

144
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,240
in a place no one knows.

145
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,680
No matter how you look at it,

146
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,800
it's just an ordinary vat.

147
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,880
But the spy

148
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,920
thinks this vat hides a huge secret.

149
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,120
So, using this vat,

150
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:22,200
we can figure out who the spy is.

151
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,240
Good idea.

152
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:24,720
Now,

153
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,840
Aqin and Yu Tong

154
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,720
are the two suspects.

155
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,320
Right?

156
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,240
Here's the plan.

157
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,880
We'll tell them separately

158
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,880
that the vat is buried somewhere.

159
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,320
Then...

160
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,720
What are you doing?

161
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,640
Burying the vat.

162
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,760
Have you ever thought

163
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,000
we don't actually have to bury the vat?

164
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,640
We just see who digs the soil,

165
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:43,360
and that proves who the spy is.

166
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,240
Right.

167
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,120
That makes sense.

168
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,360
So,

169
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,320
listen to me.

170
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,840
I'll go tell Yu Tong

171
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:51,360
the vat is buried under the tree at the east end.

172
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,560
You go tell Aqin

173
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,640
the vat is buried under the tree at the west end.

174
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:55,560
No, wait a minute.

175
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,640
Why can't I tell Aqin

176
00:05:57,680 --> 00:06:00,280
the vat is buried under the tree at the east end?

177
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:00,600
No.

178
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,080
Because I'm telling Yu Tong

179
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:04,280
the vat is buried under the tree at the east end.

180
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,240
You just tell Aqin

181
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,920
the vat is buried at the west end, and that's it.

182
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,320
No...

183
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,840
what's your basis for that?

184
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,680
Why does there need to be a basis?

185
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,920
I just said it off the top of my head.

186
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,120
We're discussing such a big matter,

187
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,320
how can you just say it off the top of your head?

188
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,120
But it's just...

189
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,040
Brother,

190
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,400
it's all the same.

191
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,680
East end or west end, it doesn't matter.

192
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,680
What matters is catching the spy.

193
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,480
The spy.

194
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,120
It's not important.

195
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,000
Got it?

196
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,400
Got it.

197
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:46,480
How is it?

198
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,120
Does it look good?

199
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,040
Arranging flowers?

200
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,280
What else did you think I was doing?

201
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,040
I...

202
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,920
It's really pretty.

203
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,400
I used to love this kind of flower.

204
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,480
I didn't expect to find it here.

205
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,280
So, did you remember something?

206
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,400
But...

207
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,680
I can't remember.

208
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,120
That's fine, too.

209
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,960
Actually, there are many of these in Daye Kingdom.

210
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:19,840
Is that so?

211
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,320
So, are you...

212
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,520
testing me?

213
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,400
Yu Tong,

214
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,880
sit down first.

215
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,280
Actually,

216
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,000
I came to find you today

217
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:43,000
because I have a secret to tell you.

218
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,520
There's more?

219
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,240
Yes.

220
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,120
Ever since he found out

221
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:50,240
that he's invincible without pants,

222
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,960
he actually demanded we all go pantless.

223
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,240
Right.

224
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,120
This is a secret.

225
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,840
Don't tell anyone.

226
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,360
That must have been a spectacular sight.

227
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,920
More than just spectacular.

228
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,800
But after the Lord found out,

229
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,400
he docked our salary for half a year.

230
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,400
Wei Qiao.

231
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,200
Brother.

232
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,400
Leaking military secrets.

233
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,680
Salary docked for half a year.

234
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,520
I did it for you.

235
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,360
Go.

236
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:11,840
Yes.

237
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,960
I have a secret to tell you.

238
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,440
A very serious one.

239
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,160
Look.

240
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:32,680
The soil on the east side hasn't been touched.

241
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,360
That's a relief.

242
00:08:37,680 --> 00:08:38,840
See? I told you.

243
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,840
Yu Tong isn't the spy.

244
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,960
Why are you talking about Yu Tong?

245
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:44,080
It means Aqin is cleared.

246
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,280
Why's that?

247
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,520
I told Aqin...

248
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,680
that the jar was buried under a tree at the east end of the village.

249
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:50,840
I told Yu Tong...

250
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,960
that this jar was buried under the tree at the east end of the village.

251
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,960
You were supposed to tell Aqin...

252
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,920
that the jar was buried at the west end of the village!

253
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,280
It doesn't matter what he said.

254
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:58,240
It doesn't matter.

255
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,360
We were supposed to say the jar was buried...

256
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,280
in different places!

257
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:00,920
Exactly!

258
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,000
Well, nobody told me!

259
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:04,680
This is all your fault.
